abstract: Western Michigan University routs Middle Tennessee State University in Bahamas Bowl, team's first bowl win.
lead_paragraph: Jamauri Bogan ran for 215 yards and four scores, powering Western Michigan to a 45-31 victory over Middle Tennessee (7-6) in the Bahamas Bowl in Nassau.
